items.name: Butter Fond O' Foods German Butter
items.details: Grass and grass-hay fed cow's milk. Hormone free milk. From cows not treated with rBST (the FDA states that no significant difference has been shown from milk derived from cows treated with artificial hormones and those not treated with artificial hormones). Pure Alpine milk. Made in Germany. For many generations the family farms in the Allgau region of Southern Germany have fed their family cows only grass and grassy-hay. This has provided excellent quality and flavor to the local cheese, milk and butter. Now from the family farms and the Fond O' Foods family this handcrafted tradition is presented to you and your family. Our Fond O' Foods pure German Butter is just that: fond of all foods, bread, crackers, baking and sauces, just to name a few. Please use in all your cooking and baking needs - Embrace the taste! www.fondofoods.com. First quality 82% butterfat. Product of Germany.
